trans-unit.source: Enables Windows-based applications to retrieve user settings from a Web settings service.
trans-unit.target: Gjør at Windows-baserte programmer til å hente brukerinnstillinger fra en webtjeneste-innstillinger.

trans-unit.source: You can use client application services to retrieve user settings from an existing Web settings service by configuring your application to use the ClientSettingsProvider class.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke programtjenester klienten til å hente brukerinnstillinger fra en eksisterende webtjeneste-innstillingene ved å konfigurere programmet for å bruke ClientSettingsProvider-klassen.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Configure Client Application Services](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [slik: Konfigurer klienten programtjenester](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: After configuration, you can get and set user settings through an application settings class derived from <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase> and configured to use the ClientSettingsProvider class.
trans-unit.target: Etter konfigurasjonen, kan du hente og angi brukerinnstillinger via en programmet klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase>og konfigurert til å bruke ClientSettingsProvider klasse.</xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase>

trans-unit.source: You can use [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] to generate a `Settings` class for your project (accessed as `Properties.Settings.Default` in C# and `My.Settings` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]).
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] til å generere en `Settings` klasse for prosjektet (som `Properties.Settings.Default` i C# og `My.Settings` i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]).

trans-unit.source: For more information about application settings, see [Application Settings Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om programinnstillinger [oversikt over programmet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve the current ClientSettingsProvider through the <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Providers%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property using the fully-qualified ClientSettingsProvider class name as a key.
trans-unit.target: Du kan hente den gjeldende ClientSettingsProvider via den <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Providers%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen ved hjelp av fullstendig ClientSettingsProvider klassenavnet som en nøkkel.</xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Providers%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can also retrieve the provider through the <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsLoadedEventArgs.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property when you handle the <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.SettingsLoaded?displayProperty=fullName> event.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også hente leverandøren via den <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsLoadedEventArgs.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Når du håndtere den <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.SettingsLoaded?displayProperty=fullName>hendelsen.</xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.SettingsLoaded?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Configuration.SettingsLoadedEventArgs.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Resets all user settings to their default values.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestiller alle brukerinnstillinger til standardverdiene.

trans-unit.source: This method is used internally by the application settings system and it not meant to be used by your application code.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden brukes internt av programmet innstillinger systemet, og det ikke ment å brukes av programkoden.

trans-unit.source: To reset Web settings to their default values, you will typically use the <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method of your project's `Settings` class (typically accessed as `Properties.Settings.Default` in C# and `My.Settings` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]).
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestill webinnstillinger til standardverdiene, vil du vanligvis bruker den <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>-metoden til prosjektets `Settings` klassen (vanligvis tilgang til som `Properties.Settings.Default` i C# og `My.Settings` i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]).</xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can also revert Web settings to the previously cached values by calling the <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Reload%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også gjenopprette webinnstillinger til tidligere bufret verdiene ved å kalle den <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Reload%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationSettingsBase.Reload%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Web settings service location.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir plassering for Web-innstillinger.

trans-unit.source: You can set the ServiceUri property in your application code, but you will typically set the value in your application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi egenskapen ServiceUri i programkoden, men du vanligvis setter verdien i programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: This enables you to change the service location without recompiling your code.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at du kan endre plassering for tjenesten uten å kompilere koden.

trans-unit.source: When you set the service location programmatically, you must specify the complete service URI, which will always end with "Profile_JSON_AppService.axd".
trans-unit.target: Når du angir plassering for tjenesten programmatisk, må du angi komplett tjeneste URI, som alltid slutter med "Profile_JSON_AppService.axd".

trans-unit.source: Occurs after the settings provider attempts to save the property values to the Web settings service.
trans-unit.target: Oppstår når innstillingene leverandøren forsøk på å lagre egenskapsverdiene til innstillinger-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This event occurs after the settings provider accesses the settings service, even if the settings were not successfully saved.
trans-unit.target: Denne hendelsen oppstår når innstillingene leverandøren har tilgang til tjenesten innstillinger, selv om innstillingene ikke ble lagret.

trans-unit.source: One reason that the provider might fail to save the settings is if the current user has been logged out.
trans-unit.target: En årsak at leverandøren kan ikke lagre disse innstillingene er hvis den gjeldende brukeren er logget.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.SettingsSavedEventArgs.FailedSettingsList%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to determine whether any settings were not successfully saved.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.SettingsSavedEventArgs.FailedSettingsList%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å fastslå om innstillinger ikke ble lagret.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.SettingsSavedEventArgs.FailedSettingsList%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This event does not occur if the settings provider cannot access the settings service, which instead causes the provider to throw a <xref:System.Net.WebException>.
trans-unit.target: Denne hendelsen oppstår ikke hvis innstillinger leverandøren ikke får tilgang til tjenesten innstillinger, som fører til at leverandøren skal returneres <xref:System.Net.WebException>.</xref:System.Net.WebException> i stedet
